MODIFICATION NOTICE
===================

This project, `cookiecutter-pypackage-secure`, is a derivative of the original
`cookiecutter-pypackage` by Audrey Roy Greenfeld and contributors:
  https://github.com/audreyfeldroy/cookiecutter-pypackage

Forked on: Tue Apr 9 17:29:16 2024 +0200  
Commit: 301eceaee466f6031b93c917cd03d6b3aced3440  
Maintainer: Gregory @Cymatickot (https://github.com/cymatickot)

Modifications include, but are not limited to:

- Migration to `pyproject.toml` and `uv` for modern builds
- Replacement of legacy CI with GitHub Actions using hardened DevSecOps stages
- Integration of SBOM generation, artefact signing, and vulnerability scanning
- Initial scaffolding for alignment with NIST SSDF, NIS2, and SLSA Level 3

All modifications are offered under the terms of the BSD 3-Clause License above.
